  "detailed_description": "The sun has stopped rising after a mysterious explosion at the top of an ancient tower.  You must gather your wits and survive eternal night in a world driven mad by apocalypse.  Every moment counts and every decision comes with consequences in the unforgiving forests of the Vlenfir Valley.  Grow, learn, adapt and equip your treasures; but be careful, something worse than death is coming for you.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Turn-based Tactics </h2><br>Plan your moves and lead your heroes to victory with superior tactics.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/extras/ad5b2e981cceb047392ee3441e1050d4.avif?t=1667490733\" width=624 height=150 /></span><br><br>Engage your foe with a tactics system focused on deep melee interactions like flanking, opportunity attacks, engagement, and competence.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/extras/3e1a48b87df4e496a0c71f1905585df2.avif?t=1667490733\" width=624 height=150 /></span><br><br>Use morale to terrify foes and bolster allies when their conviction wanes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/extras/6c5bb4b90a9448ba73f53457d8ba8c35.avif?t=1667490733\" width=624 height=150 /></span><br><br>Survive encounters with deadly bosses intent on ending your journey.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/extras/8a57557d69f9df7a3d260ef6160fa3a3.avif?t=1667490733\" width=624 height=150 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Roguelike Progression</h2><br>No one lives forever so make every choice count.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/extras/9dd74906245ddf017b832353eb5b1490.avif?t=1667490733\" width=624 height=150 /></span><br><br>Permanently unlock classes, recipes, and more through encounters and treasure rewards.  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/extras/ede99666868b6d7a2c2b36f8ec6c27e0.avif?t=1667490733\" width=624 height=150 /></span><br><br>Every playthrough features new heroes, along with new enemies to defeat, encounters to discover, and treasure to find<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/extras/94525d196b61311cce7544b3da5ec23f.avif?t=1667490733\" width=624 height=150 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Role-Playing </h2><br>Earn experience and customize your hero's skills and talents.  Add to their repertoir by discovering skill books and manuals throughout the world. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/extras/fe3c543def055873d003159c959aa7a7.avif?t=1667490733\" width=624 height=150 /></span><br><br>Use what you find or keep it to craft or sell.  Every item has value.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/extras/2d15ca83aa0428a681fbaf4f24186a7c.avif?t=1667490733\" width=624 height=150 /></span><br><br>The choices you make can change the outcome of every encounter, along with randomized results to make every playthrough different.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/extras/980304eee596bbb1d81aa079ac799391.avif?t=1667490733\" width=624 height=150 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "The sun has stopped rising after a mysterious explosion at the top of an ancient tower.  You must gather your wits and survive eternal night in a world driven mad by apocalypse.  Every moment counts and every decision comes with consequences in the unforgiving forests of the Vlenfir Valley.  Grow, learn, adapt and equip your treasures; but be careful, something worse than death is coming for you.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Turn-based Tactics </h2><br>Plan your moves and lead your heroes to victory with superior tactics.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/extras/ad5b2e981cceb047392ee3441e1050d4.avif?t=1667490733\" width=624 height=150 /></span><br><br>Engage your foe with a tactics system focused on deep melee interactions like flanking, opportunity attacks, engagement, and competence.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/extras/3e1a48b87df4e496a0c71f1905585df2.avif?t=1667490733\" width=624 height=150 /></span><br><br>Use morale to terrify foes and bolster allies when their conviction wanes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/extras/6c5bb4b90a9448ba73f53457d8ba8c35.avif?t=1667490733\" width=624 height=150 /></span><br><br>Survive encounters with deadly bosses intent on ending your journey.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/extras/8a57557d69f9df7a3d260ef6160fa3a3.avif?t=1667490733\" width=624 height=150 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Roguelike Progression</h2><br>No one lives forever so make every choice count.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/extras/9dd74906245ddf017b832353eb5b1490.avif?t=1667490733\" width=624 height=150 /></span><br><br>Permanently unlock classes, recipes, and more through encounters and treasure rewards.  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/extras/ede99666868b6d7a2c2b36f8ec6c27e0.avif?t=1667490733\" width=624 height=150 /></span><br><br>Every playthrough features new heroes, along with new enemies to defeat, encounters to discover, and treasure to find<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/extras/94525d196b61311cce7544b3da5ec23f.avif?t=1667490733\" width=624 height=150 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Role-Playing </h2><br>Earn experience and customize your hero's skills and talents.  Add to their repertoir by discovering skill books and manuals throughout the world. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/extras/fe3c543def055873d003159c959aa7a7.avif?t=1667490733\" width=624 height=150 /></span><br><br>Use what you find or keep it to craft or sell.  Every item has value.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/extras/2d15ca83aa0428a681fbaf4f24186a7c.avif?t=1667490733\" width=624 height=150 /></span><br><br>The choices you make can change the outcome of every encounter, along with randomized results to make every playthrough different.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781590/extras/980304eee596bbb1d81aa079ac799391.avif?t=1667490733\" width=624 height=150 /></span>",
